Reasoning: The paper deals with the application of control theory to partially observable Markov decision processes (POMDPs) in artificial intelligence (AI). Therefore, cs.SY (Systems and Control) is the most likely category. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) are also likely categories as POMDPs are a popular modeling framework in these fields. cs.RO (Robotics) is another possible category as POMDPs are used in robot navigation and decision making. Finally, cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses approximate methods for solving POMDPs.
